{
  "stem": "21139.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I regret that [SIGHS] move very much that I made at that time, but I had really not much choice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I did go into training and completed it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- I-- I'm not sure if the Bloomsbury House arranged something, or because it was from the Church of England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if it was free or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I'm not sure about that at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I lived in the-- in that place where I trained.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when-- on my day off, I was-- went to my youngest brother, Sigi He was in a hostel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He grew up there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Bloomsbury House-- I mean, also that organization paid for my brother, all these young people that were there, and I assume they paid for me also.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also-- I wrote-- I told the people in-- before I went to England, I-- I wrote also to the Red Cross, I remember.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they got in touch with the Bloomsbury House in London, and they found-- they found out where my sister was and my-- both my brothers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister and older brother were interned on the Isle of Man for a while in England because they were aliens, and-- but later on they were released.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Both-- my sister went to the British Army, the ATS, and my brother was in the army also for a while.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't recall if they became British citizens or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my youngest brother grew up really in Ilkley in Yorkshire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is-- the next city is Leeds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I trained in-- nearby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called-- what's it called?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was called Birley in Yorkshire, [BACKROUND NOISE] which is very close to Leeds.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
